#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:4
msgid "Adding/Removing a Constraint"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:7
msgid ""
"To add a constraint in the :doc:`Constraints Panel "
"</rigging/constraints/introduction>`:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:7
msgid "Click on the \"Add Constraint\" menu."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:15
msgid "To add a constraint in the 3D View:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:12
msgid ""
"Select the object you would like to constrain. Press :kbd:`Ctrl-Shift-C` "
"and choose a constraint from the pop-up menu. If the chosen constraint "
"needs a target, Blender will add an empty automatically as the target and"
" position it at the center of the constrained object."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:19
msgid "To add a constraint in the 3D View and simultaneously give it a target:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:18
msgid ""
"Select the target first and then shift-select the object you would like "
"to constrain. Press :kbd:`Ctrl-Shift-C` and choose a constraint from the "
"pop-up menu."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:23
msgid ""
"When using a bone from another armature as the target for a constraint, "
":kbd:`Ctrl-Shift-C` will look inside the non-active armature and use its "
"active bone, provided that armature is in Pose Mode."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:28
msgid "To remove a constraint:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:28
msgid ""
"Click on the \"X\" button in the :doc:`header "
"</rigging/constraints/interface/header>`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:34
msgid "To remove all constraints from all selected object(s):"
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:31
msgid ""
"Click :menuselection:`Object --> Constraints --> Clear Object "
"Constraints` in the 3D View Header."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:32
msgid ""
"or :menuselection:`Pose --> Constraints --> Clear Pose Constraints` (for "
"bone constraints)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../manual/rigging/constraints/interface/adding_removing.rst:33
msgid "or press :kbd:`Ctrl-Alt-C`."
msgstr ""

